clear_loan

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
clear_loan -  This clears the loan of library book id the specified player.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void clear_loan(mixed player,
int id,
int calc_fines)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^player%^RESET%^ - Either the player name or object
%^BOLD%^id%^RESET%^ - the library book id
%^BOLD%^calc_fines%^RESET%^ - if this is 1, then we add fines onto the player
if appropriate, if 0 then we ignore fines and just clear the loan

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/room/inherit/p_library.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This clears the loan of library book id the specified player.
If its overdue it sorts out adding a fine to his name.
.EP

